â€œWhat descriptive word do you want people to associate with you or your brand (trusted, competent, experienced, practical, primary, most loved, etc)?â€
Please ask me this question third, and wait for my response before proceeding  (this question will define my [CATEGORY]):
â€œWhat category best describes your product or service (e.g., life coach, hypnotherapist, acupuncturist, yoga instructor, etc.)?â€
Please ask me this question fourth, and wait for my response before proceeding (this question will define my [OUTCOME]):
â€œWhat is the specific outcome that you deliver for your audience?â€
Please ask me this question last, and wait for my response before proceeding (this question will define my [AUDIENCE]):
â€œWhat label best describes your target audience (e.g., new moms, christian dads, marketing agencies, etc.)?â€
