â—	For B2C Markets, youâ€™ll foreshadow a secret or insight to be revealed in a story. This story will be about someone who had a life-changing experience with your product or service
â—	For B2B Markets, youâ€™ll foreshadow a SECRET that will help your AUDIENCE solve their PROBLEM or achieve a BENEFIT faster, easier, or more effectively.
â—	For Information Saturated Markets, youâ€™ll foreshadow a MISTAKE thatâ€™s stopping (or could stop) your AUDIENCE from solving their PROBLEM or achieving a BENEFIT. 
â—	For Product or Service Saturated Markets, youâ€™ll foreshadow how an ALTERNATIVE solution is either failing to help them achieve a BENEFIT, failing to solve their PROBLEM, or making their PROBLEM worse. 
Next, finish this section of your ad by telling your reader that youâ€™re about to reveal the SECRET, the MISTAKE, or the insight that youâ€™ve made them curious about. 
