Market #1 Formula: B2C Products and Services 
The VSL opening for B2C markets should tell a story about someone who had a life-changing experience with your product or service. The two exceptions are if youâ€™re marketing to an information saturated market (Market Type #3), or a market thatâ€™s saturated with a product or service (SOLUTION) like yours (Market Type #4). Weâ€™ll discuss the VSL opening formulas for these two markets later in this section. 
