Element #9: Expose a Flaw (X FACTOR)
The purpose of this final element is to set our prospect up for our Offer Positioning, which will come next. Weâ€™re warning our prospect of a flaw in the general SOLUTION (product or service type) so we can tell them how our specific brand of the product or service either fixes or compensates for this flaw. 
