Next, use a â€œThis could cost youâ€¦â€ type of statement to connect the flaw youâ€™ve just exposed to something your AUDIENCE is either experiencing or likely to experience when using the SOLUTION. You can also use something that your AUDIENCE is likely to see OR hear about happening to someone else using the SOLUTION. 
Donâ€™t overdo this, or youâ€™ll poison your prospectâ€™s view of the SOLUTION and make it less likely that theyâ€™ll want your brand of it! 
