Notice how I used an â€œif___, then ___â€ transition at the end of some of these examples. This is how I anchor by OFFER to the experience Iâ€™ve just created in my readerâ€™s imagination. As you might have already guessed, these openings can also be used to create ads. Theyâ€™re especially effective when the experience of using the product or service is also the BENEFIT. 
