Notice how short and simple these openings are, but how they also do six things:
1.	They affirm your prospectâ€™s desire to experience the PROMISE.
2.	They answer your prospectâ€™s question about how long it will take (DEADLINE).
3.	They answer your prospectâ€™s EXTERNAL OBJECTION.
