www.sethczerepak.com/positioning-in-copywriting
www.sethczerepak.com/urgency-in-copywriting
Once youâ€™ve laid out these benefits, use an â€œIâ€™ve offeredâ€¦â€ statement to remind them of your GUARANTEE. 
Next, use an â€œIâ€™ve givenâ€¦â€ or â€œIâ€™ve shownâ€¦â€ or â€œIâ€™ve demonstratedâ€¦â€ statement to briefly remind them of the key elements of your Positioning message (superiority, relevance, uniqueness).  
Most importantly, remind them of the success stories youâ€™ve shared and tie this off by telling them that the people in these stories will continue enjoying their success whether your prospect buys today or not. This refocus on self-interest and the reminder that theyâ€™re being left out will snap them out of their fear, and make them eager to buy. 
