Next, use a statement like â€œThatâ€™s whyâ€¦â€ or â€œThe good news isâ€¦â€ to explain why youâ€™re inviting them to achieve the next level promise, and even magnify the BENEFITS of the original PROMISE. 
Tell them how the upsell product or service helps them achieve the next level promise without the EXTERNAL OBJECTION, and despite the INTERNAL OBJECTION by revealing the USP of your upsell offer. 
Next, future pace by telling them that instead of dealing with the costs of trying to achieve this upsell promise on their own, theyâ€™ll be enjoying the physical, financial, social, and/or emotional benefits of the upsell promise. For extra effect, tie this off by introducing  your upsell guarantee and risk removals. 
Finish with an â€œIf___, then___â€ statement to tie all of this to the qualifying statement from earlier in your opening, and to transition to the Offer Positioning section of your upsell message.  
